00:35:01,940 --> 00:35:03,220
Even so,

578
00:35:03,780 --> 00:35:05,100
I still do not hate him.

579
00:35:06,180 --> 00:35:07,980
I always feel he is like me.

580
00:35:09,300 --> 00:35:10,300
We

581
00:35:12,260 --> 00:35:13,700
admire each other.

582
00:35:17,580 --> 00:35:18,420
Dear.

583
00:35:20,340 --> 00:35:21,860
Why do you ask these things now?

584
00:35:23,060 --> 00:35:25,180
Just a whim.

585
00:35:26,180 --> 00:35:27,820
By the way, honey.

586
00:35:27,860 --> 00:35:28,860
Are we setting off

587
00:35:28,860 --> 00:35:30,300
for Zhenzhou tomorrow?

588
00:35:31,740 --> 00:35:33,780
Qiulin Xian has not yet been captured.

589
00:35:34,380 --> 00:35:36,220
There might be more trouble.

590
00:35:36,460 --> 00:35:37,300
Dear.

591
00:35:37,580 --> 00:35:40,260
On the way, you must stay
with the army's families.

592
00:35:40,940 --> 00:35:42,780
I will personally escort you back.

593
00:35:44,540 --> 00:35:45,660
Thank you, honey.

594
00:35:53,940 --> 00:35:55,220
Uncle Qiao.

595
00:35:59,660 --> 00:36:00,940
The lady is leaving.

596
00:36:00,940 --> 00:36:02,580
She let me give you this.

597
00:36:09,700 --> 00:36:13,340
(Cui Jiu is Lord Huaiyang.)

598
00:36:13,460 --> 00:36:14,820
What did the lady say?

599
00:36:14,820 --> 00:36:16,060
Did she mention me?

600
00:36:17,860 --> 00:36:20,060
That man is indeed Lord Huaiyang.

601
00:36:20,500 --> 00:36:21,860
Lord Huai?

602
00:36:37,420 --> 00:36:39,300
Miss, a letter from Xizhou has arrived.

603
00:36:39,420 --> 00:36:40,460
What did Cao Duo say?

604
00:36:40,860 --> 00:36:41,740
Did Liu Miantang

605
00:36:41,740 --> 00:36:43,060
die in Xizhou?

606
00:36:43,340 --> 00:36:44,900
Lord Huaiyang has eliminated Cao Duo.

607
00:36:45,620 --> 00:36:47,060
Liu Miantang

608
00:36:47,300 --> 00:36:48,140
has returned.

609
00:36:58,270 --> 00:36:59,230
Fresh.

610
00:37:02,980 --> 00:37:04,300
Mrs. Cui.

611
00:37:04,940 --> 00:37:06,660
Has she really returned?

612
00:37:06,660 --> 00:37:07,740
Indeed.

613
00:37:13,740 --> 00:37:15,100
Mrs. Cui.

614
00:37:17,820 --> 00:37:18,780
Still looking?

615
00:37:18,780 --> 00:37:20,260
Daring to look in front of me?

616
00:37:20,340 --> 00:37:22,020
- I dare not.
- Come home with me.

617
00:37:22,020 --> 00:37:22,860
Ouch. Ouch.

618
00:37:27,700 --> 00:37:30,420
(Cui Mansion)

619
00:37:38,500 --> 00:37:42,740
(Cui Mansion)

620
00:37:58,940 --> 00:38:00,860
(Cui Mansion)

621
00:38:21,660 --> 00:38:23,340
The war is over.

622
00:38:23,580 --> 00:38:25,860
It feels like times have changed.

623
00:38:26,180 --> 00:38:27,380
But Lingquan Town

624
00:38:27,380 --> 00:38:28,740
seems unchanged.

625
00:38:36,940 --> 00:38:37,780
Madam.

626
00:38:38,580 --> 00:38:39,740
Let's go inside.

627
00:38:42,980 --> 00:38:44,980
The wonton stand is set up here.

628
00:38:45,380 --> 00:38:46,700
When did we get

629
00:38:46,700 --> 00:38:48,460
such a good market at our door?

630
00:38:50,740 --> 00:38:51,580
Nanny Li.

631
00:38:52,100 --> 00:38:53,340
I want wontons.

632
00:38:53,740 --> 00:38:55,140
With mushroom and chestnut filling.

633
00:38:56,020 --> 00:38:56,860
Alright.

634
00:38:57,060 --> 00:38:58,060
I'll go buy them.

635
00:39:05,420 --> 00:39:06,260
Sir.

636
00:39:06,540 --> 00:39:07,420
One bowl of wontons.

637
00:39:08,140 --> 00:39:09,460
Mushroom and chestnut filling.

638
00:39:09,580 --> 00:39:10,420
Sure thing.

639
00:39:10,580 --> 00:39:11,420
Please wait a moment.

640
00:39:20,300 --> 00:39:21,140
Manager Li.

641
00:39:21,780 --> 00:39:23,860
It seems someone has been
watching Ms. Liu recently.

642
00:39:25,580 --> 00:39:26,860
The Lord already knows.

643
00:39:27,220 --> 00:39:28,060
Alright.

644
00:39:34,540 --> 00:39:35,380
Madam.

645
00:39:37,140 --> 00:39:38,020
Bicao.

646
00:39:38,140 --> 00:39:38,980
Fangxie.

647
00:39:39,380 --> 00:39:40,340
Didn't you...

648
00:39:41,340 --> 00:39:43,540
We've returned the contracts to the study.

649
00:39:43,540 --> 00:39:45,220
Bicao and I always believed

650
00:39:45,220 --> 00:39:46,700
you would return.

651
00:40:04,020 --> 00:40:06,180
Honey, you're back.

652
00:40:20,140 --> 00:40:21,740
Madam, what are you looking at?

653
00:40:23,340 --> 00:40:24,820
Why are you still standing there?

654
00:40:25,180 --> 00:40:27,060
The madam had a headache in Xizhou.

655
00:40:27,060 --> 00:40:28,620
Hurry and help her inside.

656
00:40:28,900 --> 00:40:29,740
Madam.

657
00:40:30,340 --> 00:40:32,420
Nanny Li, when will the master return?

658
00:40:32,420 --> 00:40:33,820
The master achieved military merit

659
00:40:33,820 --> 00:40:35,340
and is valued by Lord Huaiyang.

660
00:40:35,340 --> 00:40:37,420
For these few days, he must stay in the camp

661
00:40:37,420 --> 00:40:38,660
managing military affairs.

662
00:40:42,780 --> 00:40:43,620
My Lord.

663
00:40:47,380 --> 00:40:48,220
My Lord.

664
00:40:48,460 --> 00:40:49,980
The madam has safely arrived home.

665
00:40:51,260 --> 00:40:53,020
Tell the shadow guards not to slack off.

666
00:40:53,340 --> 00:40:54,260
Take good care of her.

667
00:40:54,780 --> 00:40:55,620
Yes.

668
00:40:57,180 --> 00:40:59,620
Then, what about those people?

669
00:40:59,900 --> 00:41:00,780
Kill them.

670
00:41:01,180 --> 00:41:02,500
No need to interrogate them?

671
00:41:02,860 --> 00:41:04,340
We can find out who they are.

672
00:41:04,700 --> 00:41:06,460
I already know who they are.

673
00:41:16,700 --> 00:41:17,700
Why is everyone asleep?

674
00:41:44,020 --> 00:41:44,940
Cut off their hair.

675
00:41:45,220 --> 00:41:46,060
Clean up.

676
00:41:46,220 --> 00:41:47,060
- Yes.
- Yes.

677
00:42:04,180 --> 00:42:05,580
Ms. Sun's methods

678
00:42:05,580 --> 00:42:07,060
indeed show results.

679
00:42:07,500 --> 00:42:08,900
But the Prince only asked

680
00:42:09,380 --> 00:42:11,060
for 50 people to enter the capital.

681
00:42:11,260 --> 00:42:12,380
Commander Gongsun.

682
00:42:12,380 --> 00:42:14,020
You may return to report.

683
00:42:14,420 --> 00:42:16,700
I will have everyone trained

684
00:42:16,820 --> 00:42:18,340
before the New Year.

685
00:42:18,460 --> 00:42:20,060
That will be best.

686
00:42:20,220 --> 00:42:21,180
But

687
00:42:21,180 --> 00:42:22,980
don't forget the Prince's instructions.

688
00:42:23,340 --> 00:42:24,780
It ends in Xizhou.

689
00:42:24,780 --> 00:42:26,420
Think of the big picture.

690
00:42:26,620 --> 00:42:28,660
Don't create disputes

691
00:42:28,660 --> 00:42:30,020
for personal desires.

692
00:42:30,180 --> 00:42:31,380
Of course.

693
00:42:34,700 --> 00:42:35,540
Miss.

694
00:42:36,140 --> 00:42:37,140
Why are you here?

695
00:42:37,640 --> 00:42:39,180
The package just arrived.

696
00:42:50,740 --> 00:42:53,780
(Mansion of Lord Huaiyang)

697
00:42:53,790 --> 00:42:55,020
You're finally back.

698
00:42:56,730 --> 00:42:57,660
Thinner.

699
00:42:58,960 --> 00:42:59,900
And darker.

700
00:43:01,040 --> 00:43:03,220
Xizhou's climate is harsh.

701
00:43:04,220 --> 00:43:05,300
But

702
00:43:05,420 --> 00:43:06,980
you've been back for days.

703
00:43:07,260 --> 00:43:09,060
I've been waiting day and night.

704
00:43:09,620 --> 00:43:11,540
Why did you only come home today?

705
00:43:12,380 --> 00:43:14,060
Though the war is won,

706
00:43:14,180 --> 00:43:15,220
the affairs in Zhenzhou

707
00:43:15,220 --> 00:43:16,860
cannot be delayed for a day.

708
00:43:17,300 --> 00:43:18,420
Sorry for neglecting you.

709
00:43:18,820 --> 00:43:20,060
Please don't blame me.

710
00:43:20,060 --> 00:43:22,500
Didn't we win the battle in Zhenzhou?

711
00:43:22,700 --> 00:43:24,580
Why is it still so hard?

712
00:43:25,180 --> 00:43:26,940
Have you written to the court?

713
00:43:27,060 --> 00:43:29,300
Have you expressed loyalty
to the Empress Dowager?

714
00:43:29,580 --> 00:43:30,700
Mother. Mother.

715
00:43:30,700 --> 00:43:31,540
You can

716
00:43:31,820 --> 00:43:32,740
rest assured.

717
00:43:32,740 --> 00:43:34,340
I have it all under control.

718
00:43:34,860 --> 00:43:36,060
How is your health lately,

719
00:43:36,060 --> 00:43:37,180
Mother?

720
00:43:40,340 --> 00:43:41,420
Let's not mention it.

721
00:43:42,660 --> 00:43:44,300
During the time you were away,

722
00:43:44,300 --> 00:43:45,980
the Consort Dowager couldn't eat or sleep.

723
00:43:45,980 --> 00:43:47,940
She cried every day.

724
00:43:48,900 --> 00:43:50,460
You were on the battlefield.

725
00:43:51,220 --> 00:43:53,300
Fu'er was far in the capital.

726
00:43:53,580 --> 00:43:55,580
I felt lost.

727
00:43:56,420 --> 00:43:57,620
Very distressed.

728
00:43:59,700 --> 00:44:00,700
Luckily,

729
00:44:01,180 --> 00:44:03,380
I had Binglan to keep me company.

730
00:44:20,060 --> 00:44:26,290
♪The boat drifts,
bringing back the sunset♪

731
00:44:27,290 --> 00:44:33,410
♪When we reunite, we still joke
about the cause and effect♪

732
00:44:34,400 --> 00:44:40,650
♪Who passed by, the crabapple
falls with a turn♪

733
00:44:41,780 --> 00:44:45,020
♪Loving rightly but choosing wrong♪

734
00:44:45,360 --> 00:44:49,940
♪With joys, sorrows, partings and reunions♪

735
00:44:50,540 --> 00:44:57,200
♪Everyone travels far, seeing clouds and snow♪

736
00:44:57,950 --> 00:45:01,320
♪Always hard to stay, yet easy to part♪

737
00:45:01,610 --> 00:45:04,940
♪Crossing spring waters and autumn trials♪

738
00:45:05,120 --> 00:45:11,890
♪A couple under the moonlight,
can stay together♪

739
00:45:12,270 --> 00:45:19,040
♪Long hidden in the eyes,
flickering in and out♪

740
00:45:19,540 --> 00:45:25,950
♪Let go of the flowers blooming
in the yard last night♪

741
00:45:26,790 --> 00:45:33,200
♪Let go of the waves in the stream
in half a lifetime♪

742
00:45:33,780 --> 00:45:40,400
♪Let those dust and chaos go on endlessly♪

743
00:45:41,200 --> 00:45:44,620
♪In this lifetime, my wish is to the vast sky♪

744
00:45:44,620 --> 00:45:49,720
♪There are many more♪

745
00:45:50,100 --> 00:45:56,820
♪Everyone travels far, seeing clouds and snow♪

746
00:45:57,390 --> 00:46:01,020
♪Always hard to stay, yet easy to part♪

747
00:46:01,020 --> 00:46:04,420
♪Crossing spring waters and autumn trials♪

748
00:46:04,420 --> 00:46:11,330
♪A couple under the moonlight,
can stay together♪

749
00:46:11,620 --> 00:46:18,470
♪Time flows as we dream through four seasons♪

750
00:46:18,840 --> 00:46:22,420
♪I wish to journey with you forever♪

751
00:46:22,420 --> 00:46:25,530
♪Year after year♪

752
00:46:27,260 --> 00:46:31,560
♪For many years to come♪
